Package magellan.library

Interface Addeable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Building, Faction, Group, Island, Region, Related, Ship, TempUnit, Unit, UnitContainer, ZeroUnit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompleteData, EmptyData, GameData, MagellanBuildingImpl, MagellanFactionImpl, MagellanGroupImpl, MagellanIslandImpl, MagellanRegionImpl, MagellanRelatedImpl, MagellanShipImpl, MagellanTempUnitImpl, MagellanUnitContainerImpl, MagellanUnitImpl, MagellanZeroUnitImpl, MissingData
    public interface Addeable
    This interface marks an object as addeable. Addeable objects have "attributes", i.e. Name/Value pairs.
    Version:
    1.0, 12.04.2009
    Author:
    Thoralf Rickert
